author: Sarah Al-Arshani
title: A Washington state choir rehearsal was deemed a 'super spreader event' after 45 people were infected with the coronavirus and 2 died
description: At least 45 people have been diagnosed or are suspected of having COVID-19 after a choir rehearsal in Washington state earlier this month. Sixty people attended the rehearsal on March 10. The event is considered a "super spreading" event. Visit Business Insid…
content:
Forty-five of the sixty people who attended a choir rehearsal in Washington State earlier this month were diagnosed or are suspected of having COVID-19, the Los Angeles Times reported.
